          "settings": {
            "question": "Personalization Details",
            "answer": "<p>We use sublimation ink (no vinyl), so your design will not peel or crack. Please double-check spellings of names before submitting your order.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Returns & Exchanges",
            "answer": "<p>Because each bottle is custom-made, we can't accept returns for personalization errors provided as entered. If we make a mistake, we fix it â€“ just reach out within 7 days of delivery.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq",
